  specialize w (unop U) (unop V) fU fV hU hV h
  rcases w with ‚ü®W, iU, iV, w‚ü©
  -- and put it back together again in the correct order.
  refine ‚ü®op W, fun w ‚Ü¶ fU (iU w : (unop U).1), P.res ?_ _ hU, ?_‚ü©
  ¬∑ rcases W with ‚ü®W, m‚ü©
